Paper: hep-th/9909159

Date: 1999-09-22

Title: The Goto-Imamura-Schwinger Term and Renormalization Group

Authors: Masud Chaichian and Kazuhiko Nishijima

Comments: LaTeX, 14 pages

In connection with the question of color confinement the origin of theGoto-Imamura-Schwinger term has been studied with the help of renormalizationgroup. An emphasis has been laid on the difference between theories with andwithout a cut-off.